This is XQilla, a C++ implementation of XQuery and XPath 2.0 based on Xerces-C.

Build Instructions
------------------

1. Download a source distribution of Xerces-C 3.1.2
2. Build Xerces-C

cd xerces-c-3.1.2/
./configure
make

4. Build XQilla

cd xqilla/
./configure --with-xerces=`pwd`/../xerces-c-3.1.2/
make
